1. R E Q U I R E M E N T S

In order to run this program, you need python 2.7 interpreter and libraries: thread, pickle, socket.

2. S I M P L E   T E S T

Just run :

python sever.py

 in one terminal and

python client.py 

in two more terminals. If you choose player name 'tit' or 'smejd', the player will not interactively ask you for each step but use preprogramed strategy insted.
